{
  "stem": "25178.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely no resistance whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because everybody thought they were going to, to a camp to work for Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody came with their suitcases and their knapsacks, all dressed up, took all their belongings with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no resistance whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went like cattle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's when I started to think, you know, what is going on?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why doesn't she want me to stay with her?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I mean, I saw them standing in the school, and I saw the Germans guarding the people with their-- with their guns.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that we were not just going to a work camp, like-- like they said we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think-- there was something else was going on I realized at that-- at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know what, but I knew this was not something usual to-- to bring people to go to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of the people who lived in that particular street, they were all Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before that, we lived in another street, and the people there, they were-- most of them were anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived in a-- in an apartment, on the-- in Belgium, you say first floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here, you say second floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people downstairs, they belonged to a party sympathizing with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every time my father came down the stairs to go to work, or when my mother went down the stairs, or me, or my brother, whoever-- they were waiting for us downstairs, giving us names, yelling and screaming until my father decided, that's enough.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We moved to the-- the other street, [INAUDIBLE] which was a Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the attitude in that-- in that particular time, where we lived there, was not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
